# Frontend (Vue 3)

## Stack
Vue 3 + Vite + Pinia + Dexie.js + Tailwind CSS + vue-advanced-chat

## Offline-First
1. Read from Dexie (IndexedDB) instantly
2. If online — fetch REST updates, merge into Dexie
3. Subscribe to WebSocket `/chat` for realtime

## Dexie Schema
Mirror Prisma models: `accounts`, `chatForks`, `messages`, `mediaFiles`

## Pinia Stores
- `account.ts` — Telegram accounts, hub flag
- `chat.ts` — chat forks, messages, sync with Dexie + backend

## vue-advanced-chat Wrapper
Map our `MessageSyncStatus` to custom indicators:
- `SYNCED` → "Saved to TG + Offline" ✓✓
- `OFFLINE_ONLY` / `PENDING` → "Offline only" ○

## API Base
Backend default: `http://localhost:3000`
WebSocket: `ws://localhost:3000/chat`
